import kagglehub

# Dataset path
path = Path(kagglehub.dataset_download("mostafaabla/garbage-classification"))

# Load data
dls = ImageDataLoaders.from_folder(
    path,
    train='.',
    valid_pct=0.2,
    seed=2025,
    item_tfms=Resize(224),
    batch_tfms=aug_transforms()
)

# Preview data
dls.show_batch(max_n=9, figsize=(6,6))
